OL,3,CSuspected illegal immigrants found in
OL,4,Cschool coach after returning from
OL,5,CFrance
OL,7,FA teenage girl has described her shock
OL,8,Fafter returning from a school trip to
OL,9,FFrance and discovering suspected
OL,10,Fillegal immigrants hiding in the coach
OL,11,Fon which they were travelling.
OL,13,FYear 9 student Scarlett Qiunton had
OL,14,Ftravelled to an area near Calais with
OL,15,Fher fellow pupils from Hounsdown
OL,16,FSchool in Totton, Southampton as part
OL,17,Fof a residential to improve their
OL,18,Flanguage skills.
