OL,7,FThey returned three days later, but
OL,8,Fwhen the driver opened the luggage
OL,9,Fsection, they found someone lying
OL,10,Finside among the cases.
OL,12,FScarlett said: "We got off the bus and
OL,13,Fthe compartment was opened and
OL,14,Feveryone was just trying to get their
OL,15,Fsuitcases and then I see a man sat in
OL,16,Fthe bottom.
OL,18,F"He was really calm, he was just sat
OL,19,Fstaring at us and he seemed pretty
OL,20,Fcomfy, and me and my friend were like,
OL,21,F'oh my god, there's someone in there'.
