OL,7,F"The teacher was trying to keep it all
OL,8,Fcalm and just trying to get everyone
OL,9,Fback home and obviously do her teacher
OL,10,Fstuff, but then I heard someone else
OL,11,Fin my ear say, 'oh there's two more in
OL,12,Fthere'.
OL,14,F"I sort of saw their legs, and then I
OL,15,Fran over to my mum.
OL,17,F"It was all just a bit of a shock
OL,18,Freally."
