OL,7,FScarlett managed to get her suitcase
OL,8,Fbefore then getting in the car with
OL,9,Fher mum to head home.
OL,11,FShe said despite the shock, she
OL,12,Fsympathises with the people found
OL,13,Finside the coach.
OL,15,F"I can't really blame them," Scarlett
OL,16,Fadded.
OL,18,F"They're probably just trying to get a
OL,19,Fbetter life.
