OL,7,F"I think it is important to be
OL,8,Frespectful because obviously we don't
OL,9,Freally know their background and they
OL,10,Fcould be coming from a war-torn
OL,11,Fcountry or something."
OL,13,FA spokesperson for Hampshire Police
OL,14,Fsaid: "We were called just before
OL,15,F5.15pm on Saturday 10 February to
OL,16,Freports that two people, who were
OL,17,Fpossibly illegal immigrants, had been
OL,18,Ffound at Hounsdown School in Totton.
OL,20,F"Officers have attended.
