OL,7,F"No arrests have been made."
OL,9,FA Home Office spokesperson said: "The
OL,10,FGovernment works closely with law
OL,11,Fenforcement agencies to tackle illegal
OL,12,Fmigration in all its forms.
OL,14,F"Our Illegal Migration Act will mean
OL,15,Fthat people arriving in the UK
OL,16,Fillegally are detained and promptly
OL,17,Fremoved to their country of origin or
OL,18,Fa safe third country."
OL,20,FITV Meridian has approached Hounsdown
OL,21,FSchool for a response.
